summary: [Image Description: A digital lineart drawing of Delsine Rowe from Infamous: Second Son. He’s sitting on a rock with several...
body:
[Image Description: A digital lineart drawing of Delsine Rowe from Infamous: Second Son. He’s sitting on a rock with several cans of spray paint around him, one in his hand, one next to his foot, and another at his knee. He’s staring out to the left of the page. End]

Forgot to post this when I actually drew this, but my brother and I played Infamous Second Son, and I absolutely love Delsin Rowe with my entire heart. This game is so cool.
